  {
    "start": 5.0,
    "end": 9.0,
    "text": "When I'm not sleeping, eating or at school, I'm surfing."
  },
  {
    "start": 9.0,
    "end": 12.0,
    "text": "Hi I'm Logan, I'm 10 and I love to surf."
  },
  {
    "start": 12.0,
    "end": 20.0,
    "text": "Music"
  },
  {
    "start": 20.0,
    "end": 25.0,
    "text": "My favourite manoeuvre is probably a 360."
  },
  {
    "start": 25.0,
    "end": 31.0,
    "text": "My favourite beach is McMaster's Beach and Cove of Cabana."
  },
  {
    "start": 31.0,
    "end": 35.0,
    "text": "My favourite surfer is probably Mick Fanning"
  },
  {
    "start": 35.0,
    "end": 40.0,
    "text": "because of how fast he surfs and how powerful he is in his surfing."
  },
  {
    "start": 40.0,
    "end": 42.0,
    "text": "Music"
  },
  {
    "start": 42.0,
    "end": 47.0,
    "text": "When I'm out in the water, I just think next wave, next wave, next wave"
  },
  {
    "start": 47.0,
    "end": 51.0,
    "text": "and whichever one's going to be the best, I want to get better than that."
  },
  {
    "start": 51.0,
    "end": 55.0,
    "text": "I believe what it takes to become a pro surfer"
  },
  {
    "start": 55.0,
    "end": 62.0,
    "text": "is practising, perfecting what you do and just always, always thinking about it."
  },
  {
    "start": 62.0,
    "end": 67.0,
    "text": "Music"
  },
  {
    "start": 67.0,
    "end": 73.0,
    "text": "The best achievement I've probably gotten is in the Maroobra Beach Carnival Comp."
  },
  {
    "start": 73.0,
    "end": 76.0,
    "text": "I came second in it in the finals there."
  },
  {
    "start": 76.0,
    "end": 79.0,
    "text": "I've gotten through for a few Wahoos."
  },
  {
    "start": 79.0,
    "end": 81.0,
    "text": "I'd like to thank my sponsors."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.0,
    "end": 84.0,
    "text": "Surfers Choice, FK, Life."
  },
  {
    "start": 84.0,
    "end": 85.0,
    "text": "Music"
  },
  {
    "start": 85.0,
    "end": 90.0,
    "text": "DHD, Dylan, McGrath and Ayo."
  },
  {
    "start": 90.0,
    "end": 92.0,
    "text": "I'd like to thank Dad."
  },
  {
    "start": 92.0,
    "end": 95.0,
    "text": "He's taken me to all my comps and paid for everything."
  },
  {
    "start": 95.0,
    "end": 98.0,
    "text": "Amy from Central Coast Surf Academy."
  },
  {
    "start": 98.0,
    "end": 102.0,
    "text": "She's been my coach for three years now, two years."
  },
  {
    "start": 102.0,
    "end": 105.0,
    "text": "She's really helped me develop in my surfing."
  },
  {
    "start": 105.0,
    "end": 106.0,
    "text": "I think she's awesome."
  },
  {
    "start": 106.0,
    "end": 108.0,
    "text": "They're both awesome."
